name: to 113 Repealed
text:
ARTICLE 14F
HEALTH INSURANCE RATE REGULATION--REPEALED
 
     §§431:14F-101 to 431:14F-113  REPEALED.  L 2002, c 74, §6.
 
Note
 
  The purported repeal of the L 2004, c 202, §50 amendment to §431:14F-113 on June 30, 2010, by L 2006, c 94, §1, was deleted by L 2010, c 109, §1.
  L 2006, c 154, §40 purports to amend §431:14F-105(a).
